From: Haiying Wang <Haiying.Wang@freescale.com>
Date: Mon, 7 May 2012 13:22:46 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 08/23] P5040: increase the pamu size

P5040 should use 5 pamu partitions.

Signed-off-by: Haiying Wang <Haiying.Wang@freescale.com>
[Kevin: Original patch taken from FSL
QorIQ-SDK-V1.2-SOURCE-20120614-yocto.iso ISO image.
Patch p5040ds.dts directly instead of p5040si-post.dtsi]
Signed-off-by: Kevin Hao <kexin.hao@windriver.com>
---
 arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p5040ds.dts |    2 +-
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 1 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p5040ds.dts b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p5040ds.dts
index 7bc5076..db8daf1 100644
--- a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p5040ds.dts
+++ b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p5040ds.dts
@@ -596,7 +596,7 @@
 
 		iommu@20000 {
 			compatible = "fsl,pamu-v1.0", "fsl,pamu";
-			reg = <0x20000 0x4000>;
+			reg = <0x20000 0x5000>;
 			interrupts = <
 				24 2 0 0
 				16 2 1 30>;
